name: Today's Booking
query: SELECT date as Date, time as Time, booking_type as "Booking Type:Data:150", customer as "Customer:Link/Contact:150", company_name as "Company:Link/Company:150", min_people as "Min:Int:50", exp_people as "Exp:Int:50", booking_receiver as "Booking By:Link/Contact:150", reference as "Reference:Link/Contact:150" from tabBooking where date = curdate()
